<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>L'Archipel du Savoir — 35 Mini-Jeux Complets</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Crimson+Pro:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0B1120;
    --surface: #111B2E;
    --surface2: #162035;
    --surface3: #1a2540;
    --gold: #F1C40F;
    --cyan: #00BCD4;
    --red: #E74C3C;
    --green: #2ECC71;
    --purple: #8E44AD;
    --orange: #D35400;
    --blue: #2980B9;
    --pink: #E91E63;
    --teal: #1ABC9C;
    --text: #C8D0DC;
    --text-dim: #6B7A90;
    --text-bright: #EEF1F5;
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    --legit: #3498DB;
    --pop: #E67E22;
  }
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .hero {
    text-align: center; padding: 50px 20px 30px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: -50%; left: -50%; width: 200%; height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 80%, rgba(241,196,15,0.06) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 20%, rgba(0,188,212,0.04) 0%, transparent 40%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 44px); color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 4px; text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(241,196,15,0.15); position: relative;
  }
  .hero .subtitle {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 6px;
    letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif;
  }
  .hero .meta {
    margin-top: 16px; display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .hero .meta span {
    background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 20px;
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px 80px; }
  section { margin-top: 44px; }
  section > h2 {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 1px;
    padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(241,196,15,0.12); margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .ratio-bar {
    display: flex; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; height: 8px; margin: 10px 0;
  }
  .ratio-legit { background: var(--legit); flex: 3; }
  .ratio-pop { background: var(--pop); flex: 1; }
  .ratio-legend {
    display: flex; gap: 16px; font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .ratio-legend span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; }
  .ratio-legend .dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; }
  .format-header {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px;
    margin-top: 36px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  }
  .format-sub {
    font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 4px;
  }
  .game-card {
    background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .game-card:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .game-header {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 16px 20px;
    cursor: pointer; user-select: none; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .game-header:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
  .game-num {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 6px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .game-emoji { font-size: 26px; }
  .game-title {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-bright); flex: 1;
  }
  .game-tag {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 6px;
  }
  .game-time {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 6px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .game-toggle {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-dim); transition: transform 0.3s;
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
  }
  .game-card.open .game-toggle { transform: rotate(180deg); }
  .game-body { display: none; padding: 0 20px 20px; }
  .game-card.open .game-body { display: block; }
  .game-desc {
    font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    border-radius: 10px; border-left: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .game-rules { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .game-rules h4 {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--cyan); margin-bottom: 6px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .game-rules p, .game-rules li { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.55; }
  .game-rules ul, .game-rules ol { padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .game-rules li { margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .game-reward {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: var(--gold);
    padding: 6px 12px; background: rgba(241,196,15,0.06);
    border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 12px; display: inline-block;
  }
  .game-material {
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); padding: 6px 12px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif;
  }
  .content-block {
    margin-top: 14px; padding: 14px 16px;
    background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
  }
  .content-block h5 {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .q-item {
    display: flex; gap: 8px; padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    font-size: 14px; align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .q-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .q-n {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-dim); min-width: 22px; padding-top: 2px;
  }
  .q-t { flex: 1; }
  .q-a {
    color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 11px; cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; user-select: none;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 6px;
    white-space: nowrap; align-self: center; transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .q-a:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: var(--text-bright); }
  .q-cat {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-size: 8px; font-weight: 600;
    padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 4px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    align-self: center; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .q-cat-legit { background: rgba(52,152,219,0.15); color: #5DADE2; }
  .q-cat-pop { background: rgba(230,126,34,0.15); color: #E67E22; }
  .pair-item {
    display: flex; gap: 8px; padding: 5px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03); font-size: 13px;
  }
  .pair-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .pair-a { color: var(--cyan); font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; min-width: 120px; }
  .pair-vs { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 10px; align-self: center; }
  .pair-b { color: var(--pink); font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; }
  .list-item {
    padding: 4px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    font-size: 13px; color: var(--text);
  }
  .list-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .indice-block {
    margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 10px 14px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .indice-block .ib-title {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-bright); margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .indice-block .ib-answer {
    cursor: pointer; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim);
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 6px;
    display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .indice-block .ib-answer:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: var(--text-bright); }
  .indice-line {
    font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dim); padding: 2px 0;
    display: flex; gap: 6px;
  }
  .indice-num {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold); min-width: 16px;
  }
  .top-block {
    margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 10px 14px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .top-block .top-q {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-bright); margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
  }
  .top-answers { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; }
  .top-a {
    font-size: 11px; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 6px;
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; cursor: pointer;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .top-a:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: var(--text-bright); }
  .toc { list-style: none; margin-top: 10px; }
  .toc li { padding: 5px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
  .toc li a {
    color: var(--cyan); text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; transition: color 0.2s;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  }
  .toc li a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
  .toc .toc-num { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 11px; min-width: 24px; }
  .toc .toc-format {
    font-size: 8px; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-left: auto;
  }
  .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 28px 0; }
  .expand-bar {
    display: flex; gap: 8px; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .expand-btn {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
    padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    color: var(--text-dim); transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .expand-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: var(--text-bright); }
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(130px, 1fr));
    gap: 8px; margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .stat-card {
    background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-dim);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .game-header { padding: 12px 14px; }
    .game-body { padding: 0 14px 16px; }
    .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .pair-a { min-width: 80px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
  <h1>L'ARCHIPEL DU SAVOIR</h1>
  <div class="subtitle">35 MINI-JEUX — GUIDE COMPLET DU MAÎTRE DU JEU</div>
  <div class="meta">
    <span>🎮 35 mini-jeux</span>
    <span>🎯 6 formats</span>
    <span>📚 75% culture légitime</span>
    <span>🎲 25% culture générale</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">

<!-- ═══════════ RATIO EXPLIQUÉ ═══════════ -->
<section>
  <h2>📐 Ratio des questions</h2>
  <div class="ratio-bar"><div class="ratio-legit"></div><div class="ratio-pop"></div></div>
  <div class="ratio-legend">
    <span><span class="dot" style="background:var(--legit);"></span> 75% Culture légitime — Histoire, Sciences, Littérature, Philosophie, Arts, Géographie, Politique</span>
    <span><span class="dot" style="background:var(--pop);"></span> 25% Culture générale — Pop culture, Sport, Musique actuelle, Food, Tech, Entertainment</span>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size:14px;">Les badges <span class="q-cat q-cat-legit">LÉGITIME</span> et <span class="q-cat q-cat-pop">POP/GÉ</span> marquent chaque question pour bien identifier le ratio.</p>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════ STATS ═══════════ -->
<section>
  <h2>📊 Vue d'ensemble</h2>
  <div class="stats-grid">
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">35</div><div class="stat-label">MINI-JEUX</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">6</div><div class="stat-label">FORMATS</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">10</div><div class="stat-label">TOUS VS TOUS</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">9</div><div class="stat-label">2 VS 2</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">8</div><div class="stat-label">1 VS 3</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">5</div><div class="stat-label">TOURNOI 1V1</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">2</div><div class="stat-label">COOPÉRATIF</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">1</div><div class="stat-label">COMEBACK</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════ SOMMAIRE ═══════════ -->
<section>
  <h2>📑 Sommaire des 35 mini-jeux</h2>
  <ul class="toc" id="toc-list"></ul>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════ EXPAND ═══════════ -->
<div class="expand-bar">
  <button class="expand-btn" onclick="document.querySelectorAll('.game-card').forEach(c=>c.classList.add('open'))">📖 Tout ouvrir</button>
  <button class="expand-btn" onclick="document.querySelectorAll('.game-card').forEach(c=>c.classList.remove('open'))">📕 Tout fermer</button>
  <button class="expand-btn" onclick="openRandom()">🎲 Jeu au hasard</button>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- FORMAT 1 : TOUS CONTRE TOUS (🔴)          -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="format-tvt">
  <div class="format-header" style="background:rgba(231,76,60,0.1);color:#E74C3C;">
    🔴 Tous contre tous — 4 équipes (10 jeux)
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ JEU 1 : BUZZER ═══ -->
  <div class="game-card" id="jeu-1">
    <div class="game-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
      <span class="game-num">#01</span><span class="game-emoji">🔔</span>
      <span class="game-title">Buzzer Culture</span>
      <span class="game-tag" style="background:rgba(231,76,60,0.15);color:#E74C3C;">TOUS</span>
      <span class="game-time">~5 MIN</span><span class="game-toggle">▼</span>
    </div>
    <div class="game-body">
      <div class="game-desc">Question posée à voix haute. Première équipe à taper sur la table et donner la bonne réponse gagne le point. Mauvaise réponse = éliminé pour cette question.</div>
      <div class="game-rules">
        <h4>📋 Règles</h4>
        <ol>
          <li>Le MJ lit la question lentement.</li>
          <li>Première équipe qui tape la table a 5 secondes pour répondre.</li>
          <li>Bonne → +2₽. Mauvaise → éliminée pour cette question.</li>
          <li>10 questions par manche (8 légitimes, 2 pop).</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="game-reward">🪙 +2₽ par bonne réponse</div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h5>📝 12 questions buzzer (ratio 9L / 3P)</h5>
        <div class="q-item"><span class="q-n">1</span><span class="q-t">Quel philosophe grec a fondé l'Académie à Athènes ?</span><span class="q-cat q-cat-legit">PHILO</span><span class="q-a" onclick="this.textContent=this.textContent==='Réponse'?'Platon':'Réponse'">Réponse</span></div>
        <div class="q-item"><span class="q-n">2</span><span class="q-t">Quel traité de 1648 a mis fin à la guerre de Trente Ans ?</span><span class="q-cat q-cat-legit">HIST</span><span class="q-a" onclick="this.textContent=this.textContent==='Réponse'?'Traités de Westphalie':'Réponse'">Réponse</span></div>
        <div class="q-item"><span class="q-n">3</span><span class="q-t">Quel est l'élément chimique de symbole Fe ?</span><span class="q-cat q-cat-legit">SCIENCE</span><span class="q-a" onclick="this.textContent=this.textContent==='Réponse'?'Le fer':'Réponse'">Réponse</span></div>
        <div class="q-item"><span class="q-n">4</span><span class="q-t">Qui a écrit « Du contrat social » en 1762 ?</span><span class="q-cat q-cat-legit">PHILO</span><span class="q-a" onclick="this.textContent=this.textContent==='Réponse'?'Jean-Jacques Rousseau':'Réponse'">Réponse</span></div>
        <div class="q-item"><span class="q-n">5</span><span class="q-t">Quel peintre a réalisé « La Liberté guidant le peuple » ?</span><span class="q-cat q-cat-legit">ART</span><span class="q-a" onclick="this.textContent=this.textContent==='Réponse'?'Eugène Delacroix':'Réponse'">Réponse</span></div>
        <div class="q-item"><span class="q-n">6</span><span class="q-t">Quel détroit sépare l'Europe de l'Asie au niveau d'Istanbul ?</span><span class="q-cat q-cat-legit">GÉO</span><span class="q-a" onclick="this.textContent=this.textContent==='Réponse'?'Le Bosphore':'Réponse'">Réponse</span></div>
        <div class="q-item"><span class="q-n">7</span><span class="q-t">Quel scientifique a découvert la structure de l'ADN avec Watson ?</span><span class="q-cat q-cat-legit">SCIENCE</span><span class="q-a" onclick="this.textContent=this.textContent==='Réponse'?'Francis Crick (et Rosalind Franklin)':'Réponse'">Réponse</span></div>
        <div class="q-item"><span class="q-n">8</span><span class="q-t">Quel empire a bâti la Cité interdite de Pékin ?</span><span class="q-cat q-cat-legit">HIST</span><span class="q-a" onclick="this.textContent=this.textContent==='Réponse'?'La dynastie Ming':'Réponse'">Réponse</span></div>
        <div class="q-item"><span class="q-n">9</span><span class="q-t">Quelle est la capitale de l'Australie ?</span><span class="q-cat q-cat-legit">GÉO</span><span class="q-a" onclick="this.textContent=this.textContent==='Réponse'?'Canberra':'Réponse'">Réponse</span></div>
        <div class="q-item"><span class="q-n">10</span><span class="q-t">Quel pays a gagné la Coupe du monde de football 2022 ?</span><span class="q-cat q-cat-pop">SPORT</span><span class="q-a" onclick="this.textContent=this.textContent==='Réponse'?'Argentine':'Réponse'">Réponse</span></div>
        <div class="q-item"><span class="q-n">11</span><span class="q-t">Quel rappeur américain a sorti l'album « DAMN. » ?</span><span class="q-cat q-cat-pop">POP</span><span class="q-a" onclick="this.textContent=this.textContent==='Réponse'?'Kendrick Lamar':'Réponse'">Réponse</span></div>
        <div class="q-item"><span class="q-n">12</span><span class="q-t">Dans quel film Simba est-il le personnage principal ?</span><span class="q-cat q-cat-pop">POP</span><span class="q-a" onclick="this.textContent=this.textContent==='Réponse'?'Le Roi Lion':'Réponse'">Réponse</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ JEU 2 : CHRONO-LISTE ═══ -->
  <div class="game-card" id="jeu-2">
    <div class="game-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
      <span class="game-num">#02</span><span class="game-emoji">📝</span>
      <span class="game-title">Chrono-Liste</span>
      <span class="game-tag" style="background:rgba(46,204,113,0.15);color:#2ECC71;">TOUS</span>
      <span class="game-time">~5 MIN</span><span class="game-toggle">▼</span>
    </div>
    <div class="game-body">
      <div class="game-desc">Thème annoncé. Chaque équipe à tour de rôle a 5 secondes pour donner une réponse valide. Répétition = éliminé. Dernier debout gagne.</div>
      <div class="game-reward">🪙 1er : +5₽ · 2e : +3₽ · 3e : +1₽</div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h5>📝 16 thèmes (12 légitimes / 4 pop)</h5>
        <div class="list-item">1. 📚 Auteurs français de littérature <span class="q-cat q-cat-legit">LIT</span></div>
